### 4.3 Core Features (Phase 1 вҖ” MVP)

1. **User Authentication** вҖ” Sign up / Sign in (email + Google), Firebase JWT for all protected API calls
2. **Product Catalog** вҖ” Browse 39+ real listings with images, ratings, condition tags, and categories
3. **Search & Filter** вҖ” Search by keyword, filter by category, condition, sort by price/rating
4. **Product Detail** вҖ” Full description, specs, merchant info, availability calendar, reviews
5. **Booking Flow** вҖ” Select rental dates вҶ’ calculate total cost + deposit вҶ’ Razorpay checkout
6. **Merchant Dashboard** вҖ” Add/edit/remove listings, view active bookings and earnings
7. **Messaging** вҖ” In-platform chat between renter and owner before/after booking
8. **Admin Panel** вҖ” View all users, products, and bookings; manage disputes

### 4.4 Data Model

```
users:        { uid, email, name, role: renter|merchant|admin, verified, createdAt }
products:     { merchant(uid), title, description, category, pricePerDay, securityDeposit,
                condition, images[], rating, reviewCount, specs{}, status, createdAt }
bookings:     { renter, product, startDate, endDate, totalDays, totalCost, deposit,
                status: PENDING|CONFIRMED|ACTIVE|RETURNED|CANCELLED, createdAt }
reviews:      { product, reviewer, rating, comment, createdAt }
chats:        { participants[], messages[{ sender, text, timestamp }] }
payments:     { booking, razorpayOrderId, razorpayPaymentId, amount, status, createdAt }
```

### 4.5 UI Design System

- **Dual Theme**: Light mode (clean white + blue) and Dark mode (deep navy), switchable live
- **Glassmorphism**: Frosted-glass sticky navigation with `backdrop-filter: blur()`
- **Typography**: `Plus Jakarta Sans` вҖ” weights 400 / 600 / 800
- **Gradients**: Primary `#2563eb вҶ’ #7c3aed`, Accent `#f59e0b вҶ’ #d97706`
- **Motion**: Staggered slide-in animations for menus, hover lift on cards

---

## 5. Unique Value Propositions

| Feature | LendeX | Typical Classified Sites |
|---|---|---|
| Security deposit management | вң… Automated via Razorpay | вқҢ Manual / cash |
| Verified merchant badges | вң… Admin-approved | вқҢ None |
| In-platform messaging | вң… Real-time capable | вқҢ External WhatsApp |
| Dynamic pricing (per day) | вң… Customizable | вқҢ Fixed price / negotiation |
| Professional UI | вң… Amazon-grade | вқҢ Generic listings |
| Rental status tracking | вң… PENDING вҶ’ RETURNED flow | вқҢ None |

---

## 6. Known Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Fake listings / fraud | Admin verification layer + security deposit system |
| Item damage disputes | Pre/post rental condition photos stored in Firebase Storage |
| Payment failures | Razorpay webhook-based verification вҖ” order confirmed only after payment |
| Firestore lacks full-text search | In-memory title/description filter implemented on backend |

---

## 7. How to Run (Development)

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo and install dependencies
cd rental-marketplace/backend
npm install

# 2. Configure environment variables
# Edit backend/.env with Firebase and Razorpay credentials

# 3. Start the server
npm run dev
# вҶ’ Server runs on http://localhost:5000

# 4. Seed the database (run once)
node seed.js
# вҶ’ Seeds 39 premium product listings

# 5. Visit the app
# Open http://localhost:5000 in your browser
```

